{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ebed56e5f1","title":"周恩来江青听取铁路会议代表汇报时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f6eaf7d769","index":0,"year":1968,"month":4,"day":5,"articleId":"ebed56e5f1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"薄一波","id":"d54ab0cc80","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"江青，本世纪初国内老左编","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"10e6e6b72d","type":"title","text":"周恩来江青听取铁路会议代表汇报时的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f0ae1f8be","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在要集中目标，批判吕正操、武竞天、孙大光（注：交通部前副部长）。","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c6b7c992e","type":"paragraph","text":"（杨杰同志插话解释说：武竞天他不是要翻案吗？写了个所谓检讨，检讨可以概括为三句话：一个他不承认是走资派，一个他不承认是叛徒，三是不承认与薄一波有什么关系──三个不承认，实际上是地地道道的右倾翻案！）","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"661ff6b9cb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：结合批判本单位特务、叛徒、死不悔改的走资派以及刘、邓、陶、彭、罗、陆、杨，结合起来，使群众站在毛主席革命路线上，方向就一致了。","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f09e80aa02","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：总的来讲，现在是反右，反对右倾思潮，但是要做具体分析（讲了两遍）极“左”和右本质是一样的，都是对准以毛主席为首，林副主席为副的无产阶级司令部，都是要搞资本主义复辟。铁路就是右倾，《今日哥达纲领》就是右倾，就是要推翻无产阶级专政。","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d5a42cb9f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：无政府主义，反革命经济主义，也都是右倾。","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28c6d58569","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：搞无政府主义，不出勤，这是什么形“左”实右呢？！连个影都没有，就是右倾。","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"ebed56e5f1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":597,"end":597}}}},"__N_SSG":true}